This package installs an optional daemon script at:
/etc/rc.d/rc.sonarr

The default init runs as sonarr:sonarr with its data directory as:
/var/lib/sonarr

You can edit the init file directly, or you can change the default
user and group at build time:
    
    # NZBGET_USER=user NZBGET_GROUP=group DATA_DIR=/path/to/dir \
        ./nzbget.SlackBuild
